Package uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.tuple

Interface Tuple<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - The type of reference used by the underlying data structure to access data values.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Object>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayTuple, MapTuple, ReferenceArrayTuple, ReflectiveTuple, Tuple1, Tuple2, Tuple3, Tuple4, Tuple5, TupleN
    public interface Tuple<R>
extends Iterable<Object>
    A Tuple provides a map-like interface to any data structure.
